Class MemoryStringRepository

  • dev.b3nedikt.restring.repository.MemoryStringRepository
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StringRepository

    public class MemoryStringRepository
implements StringRepository

    A StringRepository which keeps the strings ONLY in memory.

    it's not ThreadSafe.
